Interface FormatConstants

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DjatokaImageMigrator, ExtractorFactory, FormatFactory, OpenURLJP2Datastream, OpenURLJP2KMetadata, OpenURLJP2KService, OpenURLJP2Ping, OpenURLJP2XML

    public interface FormatConstants
    Format Writer/Reader Constants. Defines default image writer implementations and mimetypes / ext. associated with image format.
